{"tid":2049184,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"周日九龍區遊行遭警方發出反對通知書","createTime":"2020-06-03T09:35:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T11:27:07.000Z","uid":3302,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"919c544f2665f6ec670e0335f076f2e5ca97bf3f","tid":2049184,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T09:35:07.000Z","msg":"團體「學生動源」計劃在周日發起的九龍區大遊行被警方反對，下午已收到警方發出的反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n「學生動源」引述警方表示，基於限聚令延長、類似議題遊行從去年6月起，曾多次爆發嚴重暴力衝突，而「學生動源」主張勇武抗爭，過去相同議題遊行最終都會作出嚴重暴力違法行為，破壞社會安寧。<br />\n<br />\n「學生動源」說，對警方發出反對通知書理由表示強烈不滿，無理指控「學生動源」計劃煽動他人於合法遊行作出違法行為，強調根據《基本法》，香港居民有集會、遊行、示威的自由，警方無權禁止任何有關活動。"},{"pid":"590d897643495f01a828aa92b97fb4f9a34e67d4","tid":2049184,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T09:35:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529975-20200603.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529975-20200603.htm&d=ZttPR3oQiG8LQafLEcup%2BLtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=fe3fecea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529975-20200603.htm&h=48e746a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529975-20200603.htm</a>"},{"pid":"60b4357e4f5a4e7ec33d2f2d8380736b6f089fd7","tid":2049184,"uid":3302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T09:35:51.000Z","msg":"如果次次都出反對通知書 係咪以後唔洗出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f740b600aada06bafcc07761e4b7260cd48028","tid":2049184,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T09:36:23.000Z","msg":"姐係其他地方唔反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9be51eebbfba6743eaf1b18e68671615c2533d","tid":2049184,"uid":186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"60b4357e4f5a4e7ec33d2f2d8380736b6f089fd7","tid":2049184,"uid":3302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,